%% Onboarding — first-run setup wizard for a newly created business (Owner only)
%% Entered from dashboard-access.mmd when Onboarding is incomplete.
%% Steps are skippable; progress is saved so the Owner can resume later.
flowchart TD
    Start([Owner enters setup wizard]) --> Resume{Resume in progress?}
    Resume -->|Yes| LastStep[Jump to last incomplete step]
    Resume -->|No| Business

    Business[Step 1 — Business profile<br/>name, type, address, timezone] --> SaveBiz[(Save progress)]
    SaveBiz --> Hours

    Hours[Step 2 — Operating hours] --> SaveHours[(Save progress)]
    SaveHours --> Services

    Services[Step 3 — Add services<br/>name, duration, price] --> SvcAdded{At least one service?}
    SvcAdded -->|No, skip| Staff
    SvcAdded -->|Yes| SaveSvc[(Save progress)] --> Staff

    Staff[Step 4 — Invite staff<br/>email + role +<br/>services they can perform] --> InviteSent[/Send invites — see staff-management.mmd/]
    InviteSent --> SaveStaff[(Save progress)]
    SaveStaff --> Settings

    Settings[Step 5 — Dashboard settings<br/>branding, booking rules, notifications] --> SaveSettings[(Save progress)]
    SaveSettings --> Review

    Review[Review summary] --> Confirm{Finish setup?}
    Confirm -->|Edit a step| LastStep
    Confirm -->|Finish| MarkComplete[Mark onboarding complete]
    MarkComplete --> Dashboard([Go to full dashboard])

    LastStep --> Business
